lead_paragraph: Arsenal have a gilt-edged opportunity to kick a self-destructive Champions League habit when they host Paris St Germain on Wednesday knowing victory will seal top spot in Group A.

headline.print_headline: Arsenal Seek Win to Kick Costly Runners-Up Habit
